        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"Then he must have jumped down upon the grass, where he knew he would not leave any footprint. He must have walked very quietly on the grass up to the tree where the traveler was sleeping, and stolen the money.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
