        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"First, about the camel being blind in his right eye.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_111913_000021_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/111913/7946_111913_000021_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "He had nibbled at the shrubs and bushes growing on the left side of the road, for at each bite I found the leaves cut off clean by his teeth.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
