        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "So I knew that he was lame in that foot.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_111913_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/111913/7946_111913_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"That is also very clever of you,\" the judge said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "Next day, as we were at breakfast at the Mansion, the masons and carpenters came.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
