        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "Curiously enough, one of them brought a note from Martin, asking if it would be convenient for him to bring a stranger, with valuable information, to see mr Oakes that morning; and the man found it convenient to drop into town a little later and incidentally to meet Martin and let him know that Oakes expected him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"Looks as though I am going to hold a reception this morning,\" said Oakes: \"The Chief of Police making an engagement last night for an interview this morning, and now Martin asking for another.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"What is Martin doing up here?\" asked Moore.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"Well, don't get impatient.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "He has something important, anyway.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "It was not long before Martin and mr Elliott were with us.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "Oakes received Elliott in a most agreeable manner, which placed us all at ease.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "Also he was sure it must be of great value, since the gentleman had travelled all the way from New York to place him in possession of it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "And this was said before any information was given.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000006_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000006_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "We saw that our friend was a diplomat.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "Looking out of the window at that moment, I espied Hallen coming up the walk.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"Good!\" said Oakes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"Now, mr Elliott, will you kindly retire with dr Moore, while Stone, Martin and I hear what the Chief has to say.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "When Hallen came up, he seemed very cordial, but worried, and made no attempt to disguise the fact that he anticipated trouble with the unruly element in Mona by Saturday night.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"You see,\" he said, \"we are few here, and I have been kept busy with the brewing uneasiness in town and cannot handle the murder affair satisfactorily.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "I have come to ask you to help me, if you are sufficiently at leisure.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "We cannot get any clues at all, save that the man was killed by a bullet of large calibre in the hands of a good shot, as the distance from which it was fired would seem to show.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "The people must be diverted, and more must be done at once than I can do.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "Will you help me?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"Yes,\" said Oakes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"Of course!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"Hello, what ails your head?\" said the Chief, after thanking him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "And then Oakes told him as much as was necessary of the events of the day before.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "They understood one another-they were in similar lines of business.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "Elliott was admitted unreservedly to our councils, especially as Oakes knew that he held the keys to the conviction of the assassin-the witness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "Oakes, in his fluent style, acquainted the Chief with the fact that the negro was already under surveillance and that, in his opinion, he should be brought to Mona for further examination.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "It would be unwise to let the populace know we have him now; they might infer he was the murderer and violence would certainly be done him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "At present, I have all I can do to keep order in the town,\" said Hallen.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "life-long friends are suspicious of one another and business is nearly at a standstill.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "One must always take account of the actions and reasonings of communities. Emotional waves rush through them as through individuals sometimes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000023_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000023_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "Look at history, and consider the waves of religion, emotional in character, that have occurred.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"Certainly,\" Oakes replied.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"It is most important.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "I myself had frequently had cause to study such mental processes in the practice of my profession, but I was amazed at the knowledge shown by Oakes, and stated in such a broad, untechnical manner.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "The man was no ordinary one, to be sure, but I had scarcely expected him to show such education in these matters.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "dr Moore broke the silence.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"You are a lalapazooza, Oakes.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "Oakes did not notice the remark, but said: \"I don't know what other men do, but I have tried to bear in mind such things.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "\"It seems to me,\" continued Hallen, \"that your work here at the Mansion will soon lead to results, and I trust that you will find time to consider the murder also.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7946_116281_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7946/116281/7946_116281_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7946",
        "content": "And thus Quintus Oakes became the leader in the unravelling of the Mark murder mystery.",
